    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sivi's Factory</strong> is a dark first-person horror game where you play as Felix, desperately searching for his brother in a massive scientific factory. From the very first steps, you're surrounded by a mysterious atmosphere, with dangers lurking around every corner.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/9faf4d4bcfb3a10ab7c3a553a4f37eff.poster.avif?t=1727563724\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/9faf4d4bcfb3a10ab7c3a553a4f37eff.webm?t=1727563724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/9faf4d4bcfb3a10ab7c3a553a4f37eff.mp4?t=1727563724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The factory is a labyrinth of various workshops, hidden passages, and unknown rooms, where every new discovery brings new threats.</strong> You'll need to solve puzzles, explore dark rooms, and fight off a terrifying enemy that chases you throughout the factory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/437753e8ea3629d3dda36d692b9fe5b1.poster.avif?t=1727563724\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/437753e8ea3629d3dda36d692b9fe5b1.webm?t=1727563724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/437753e8ea3629d3dda36d692b9fe5b1.mp4?t=1727563724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>One of the unique mechanics in the game is a watch with a cartridge that can be printed using a 3D printer to unlock various functions to progress through levels.</strong> Printers will also help create key items, such as access cards, which will open new locations and allow you to delve deeper into the depths of the factory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/f234489f4b00354ecc5546725b010406.poster.avif?t=1727563724\" width=620 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/f234489f4b00354ecc5546725b010406.webm?t=1727563724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3133610/extras/f234489f4b00354ecc5546725b010406.mp4?t=1727563724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>You'll encounter four unique locations, each filled with its own secrets and traps.</strong> Dive deeper into the complex, solve engaging puzzles, and uncover the truth about what happened at the factory, where your brother is... and what secrets hide in the shadows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Get ready for a tense atmosphere, challenging puzzles, and dangerous battles in Sivi's Factory.</strong></p>",
